# __PROJECT_NAME__

A [Vulse](https://github.com/ekrist1/vulsecms) project.

## Develop

```sh
pnpm install
pnpm dev      # admin SPA on http://localhost:5173
```

Vulse is a **headless CMS**. The admin SPA and HTTP API are bundled here;
your public-facing site lives in a separate Astro / Next / SvelteKit project
that fetches content from `/api/public/*`. See
[docs/frontend-foundation.md](https://github.com/ekrist1/vulsecms/blob/main/docs/frontend-foundation.md)
for the recipe.

## Build & run in production

```sh
pnpm build
PORT=3000 pnpm start
```

## Upgrade Vulse

```sh
pnpm up "@vulse/*"
```

Then read the [upgrade guide](https://github.com/ekrist1/vulsecms/blob/main/docs/upgrading.md)
for any breaking-change notes between versions.

## Where things live

| Path                  | Purpose                                        |
| --------------------- | ---------------------------------------------- |
| `vulse.config.ts`     | Database & blueprints directory                |
| `blueprints/`         | Content collection definitions                 |
| `modules/`            | Your custom extensions (routes, listeners…)    |
| `server/server.ts`    | The server entry — composes `@vulse/host`      |
| `src/main.ts`         | Admin SPA entry                                |

Read [docs/architecture.md](https://github.com/ekrist1/vulsecms/blob/main/docs/architecture.md)
for the full extension model.
